flowchart TD
    A([Admin: Simulations → Red Team]) --> B[Click Create Campaign]
    B --> C[Step 1: Channel Selection]

    C --> D{Channels selected?}
    D -- SMS only --> E1[Single-channel mode]
    D -- WhatsApp only --> E2[Single-channel mode]
    D -- SMS + WhatsApp --> E3[Multi-channel mode]
    D -- WhatsApp API template-only --> E4[WhatsApp constrained to pre-approved templates]

    E1 & E2 & E3 & E4 --> F[Step 2: Audience]

    F --> G{Targeting mode?}
    G -- Groups --> H[Group picker + per-channel coverage breakdown]
    G -- Individuals --> I[People-search + per-user channel chips]
    G -- Both --> J[Group picker + people-search + overlap detection]

    H & I & J --> K{Coverage: any channel?}
    K -- 0% all channels for full audience --> L[Hard block: 0% coverage\nContinue disabled\nShow resolution path]
    L --> F
    K -- Partial coverage --> M[Warning callout: N targets unreachable\nAdmin can proceed]
    K -- Full coverage --> N[Continue]
    M --> N

    N --> O[Step 3: Template + Message]
    O --> P{Multi-channel?}
    P -- Yes --> Q[SMS tab + WhatsApp tab in preview panel]
    P -- No --> R[Single-channel preview panel]
    Q & R --> S{WhatsApp link detected?}
    S -- Yes --> T[Link preview warning callout\nAdmin acknowledges]
    S -- No --> U[Continue]
    T --> U

    U --> V[Step 4: Compliance Pre-flight]
    V --> W{All items ✓?}
    W -- Any item ✗ unresolved --> X[Block: show resolution CTA per item\nContinue disabled]
    X --> V
    W -- Any item ⚠ Pending --> Y[Soft warning: setup in progress\nContinue enabled\nCampaign saved as draft on launch attempt]
    W -- All ✓ --> Z[Ready to proceed]
    Y & Z --> AA[Step 5: Delivery]

    AA --> AB{Multi-channel?}
    AB -- Yes --> AC[Configure fallback routing:\nFall back to SMS /\nSurface error only /\nSilent exclude]
    AB -- No --> AD[Schedule + spread only]
    AC & AD --> AE[Step 6: Remediation]

    AE --> AF{Suppress remediation?}
    AF -- ON default --> AG[Suppression confirmed\nNo automation fires]
    AF -- Admin toggles OFF --> AH[Configure if/then rules per channel event]
    AG & AH --> AI[Step 7: Test Send]

    AI --> AJ{Multi-channel?}
    AJ -- Yes --> AK[Test SMS: send + confirm\nTest WhatsApp: send + confirm]
    AJ -- No --> AL[Test single channel: send + confirm]

    AK --> AM{All channel checkboxes confirmed?}
    AL --> AM
    AM -- No --> AN[Admin skips with strong warning modal]
    AM -- Yes --> AO[Continue]
    AN --> AO

    AO --> AP[Step 8: Review + Launch]
    AP --> AQ{Hard blocks present?}
    AQ -- Yes: 0% coverage or compliance ✗ --> AR[Launch disabled\nInline error + back to blocking step]
    AQ -- No --> AS{Compliance acknowledgment checked?}
    AS -- No --> AT[Launch disabled\nTooltip: confirm before launching]
    AS -- Yes --> AU[Launch Campaign]

    AU --> AV[Campaign detail: Sending status\nPer-channel delivery counts populate]

    AV --> AW{Delivery events}
    AW -- SMS delivered + clicked --> AX[red_team_sms_link_clicked recorded\nDebrief page served]
    AW -- WhatsApp delivered + clicked --> AY[red_team_whatsapp_link_clicked recorded\nDebrief served in WhatsApp in-app browser]
    AW -- WhatsApp failed + fallback ON --> AZ[SMS fallback send triggered\nFallback event recorded separately]
    AW -- WhatsApp failed + surface error --> BA[Per-user error row: WhatsApp failed — reason]
    AW -- WhatsApp failed + silent exclude --> BB[User excluded from delivery count silently]

    AX & AY & AZ --> BC{Remediation suppressed?}
    BA & BB --> BC
    BC -- Yes --> BD[No automation fires\nTarget not notified]
    BC -- No --> BE[Remediation rule evaluated\nTraining assigned or manager notified per rule]

    BD & BE --> BF([Campaign Completed\nPer-channel stats finalized\nPer-user results table fully populated])

    style L fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#7f1d1d
    style AR fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#7f1d1d
    style X fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f
    style Y fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f
    style AN fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f
    style AT fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f
    style BF fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d
    style A fill:#f1f5f9,stroke:#64748b
